430
00:28:50,330 --> 00:28:52,860
Aku baru saja merasakannya
bahwa suasana hati Hui sedang buruk.

431
00:28:53,620 --> 00:28:55,050
Ada peluang bagus

432
00:28:55,050 --> 00:28:56,720
